  <brief_title>Cerebral Near Infrared Spectroscopy During Blood Sampling From a Peripheral Artery Catheter in Preterm Infants</brief_title>
  <official_title>Measurement of Cerebral Oxygenation With Near Infrared Spectroscopy During Blood Sampling From a Peripheral Artery Catheter in Preterm Infants With Gestational Age &lt;37+0</official_title>
  <sponsors>
